{"tid":1511503,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"十點鳩嗌","createTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T13:57:58.000Z","uid":272654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"57ddeef25014922d9c19816ea0e74ae50d2abaa6","tid":1511503,"uid":272654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:22.000Z","msg":"頭先放工行到返屋企附近<br />\n係到望住個鐘 2159 好緊張 唔知有冇人會嗌<br />\n2200 都仲未有&hellip;心諗 唉呢邊啲可能都冇乜人嗌<br />\n諗住鼓起勇氣嗌完自己覆自己之際<br />\n<br />\n巴絲們就出黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗰下企係條街隔離全部都係人我都照嗌<br />\n多謝你地比勇氣我 仲有所有一路以為冇人陪嘅大家<br />\n<br />\n（拍唔切片  嗌到而家都未完）"},{"pid":"3bc8cc535e6c7dcecc49a0257018b516a921329e","tid":1511503,"uid":230890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:22:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"40f6b5017299c44f308de83e20b869068cd11f48","tid":1511503,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:23:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"267fa77df33ad8fea38fcc5040c7a9abc717fddc","tid":1511503,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:23:12.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"1f1cbf3c7430132dfd747664c5143ef260cd1434","tid":1511503,"uid":272654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"要準備2230嗰場啦"},{"pid":"6c171da6a1d23f7b0038e3ecb790b0086b21f45a","tid":1511503,"uid":306807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T14:27:35.000Z","msg":"不如一齊讀出五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n[五大訴求]透過吶喊幫藍絲上堂<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511488</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"865b5c6b172ac775f0ed045ef2f3364ff6b896c8","tid":